reviews.text: Not much more than a platform now but does have plenty of the old sidings,  station house and other bits to see - level crossing to a bridle path along the coast and of course golf course! Still a used line with daily trains stopping.

The international airport comes in handy here, and it's great if you work for Google, Microsoft, Apple, Yahoo, Samsung or BMW, as all their headquarters are here. 
My only advice would be to get there early, as it can become quite manic.
Travelling with your kids? No problem. Bet you didn't know they had their own Disneyland too?

Great station.  No queuing at all.

Great places to get a bite to eat McDonald's, KFC, Costa, Pret, Wagama's,  Pizza Express  and plenty more to choose from at this Station.
Quaint station with remnants of times past
beautifully maintained station, although few passengers
